    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/82e754e62bbd5971302da4eb3f0b1977.poster.avif?t=1771618297\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/82e754e62bbd5971302da4eb3f0b1977.webm?t=1771618297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/82e754e62bbd5971302da4eb3f0b1977.mp4?t=1771618297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Crafting System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather materials and craft tools, items, and equipment for exploration or other tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/485cd1a61aaaab43c68d6cf3f4e447ef.poster.avif?t=1771618297\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/485cd1a61aaaab43c68d6cf3f4e447ef.webm?t=1771618297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/485cd1a61aaaab43c68d6cf3f4e447ef.mp4?t=1771618297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Cooking Recipes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect ingredients and cook meals that restore hunger. From basic eating options to complex cooking recipes featuring mini game like mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/f77946a525a7d8f062b497263470884f.avif?t=1771618297\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras_big/f77946a525a7d8f062b497263470884f.avif?t=1771618297 width=800 height=487 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Open World Exploration</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover Carden's vast and diverse landscapes at your own pace, uncovering its secrets and hidden locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/b8e516a5486df2d7cf5e1ddf6ac1bf94.avif?t=1771618297\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras_big/b8e516a5486df2d7cf5e1ddf6ac1bf94.avif?t=1771618297 width=800 height=487 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Self-Discovery and Storytelling</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in a narrative-driven experience where your choices and interactions shape your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/9acc6c232c2ffb88e07e655fbe4321be.avif?t=1771618297\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras_big/9acc6c232c2ffb88e07e655fbe4321be.avif?t=1771618297 width=800 height=487 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Farming and Gardening</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cultivate crops and plants that can be used for cooking, crafting, or traded for other resources. Farming plots can be built and managed featuring mini game like mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/44068b311c98655d4fde8e75b3116498.avif?t=1771618297\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras_big/44068b311c98655d4fde8e75b3116498.avif?t=1771618297 width=800 height=487 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collecting and managing Resources</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search the island for food, supplies, resources and so much more to advance research and uncover the island's history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/f499b982d49604891f0d2776502d4bb4.avif?t=1771618297\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras_big/f499b982d49604891f0d2776502d4bb4.avif?t=1771618297 width=800 height=487 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hidden Areas and Secrets</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore off-the-beaten-path locations to discover hidden caves, ancient ruins, or rare resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras/f75205764861e9eba2b8beb515b059f4.avif?t=1771618297\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241120/extras_big/f75205764861e9eba2b8beb515b059f4.avif?t=1771618297 width=800 height=487 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quest System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on a variety of quests from NPCs, ranging from simple fetch quests to complex multi-stage missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Environmental Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles scattered across the island that unlock new areas or grant access to resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fishing Mechanics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish in various bodies of water, each with unique species to collect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Digging for Treasure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a shovel to dig for buried treasures, fossils, and minerals that can be sold, used, or researched.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Axe and Pickaxe Tools</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilise tools like axes and pickaxes to chop wood, mine minerals, and clear obstacles in the environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TNT and Explosives</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use TNT to clear large obstacles, open new paths, or uncover hidden areas in the more rugged parts of the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Trading with NPCs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade resources, items, and crafted goods with local NPCs to obtain rare materials and unique upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shop Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operate a shop where you can sell crafted items, farm produce, or rare finds to visiting explorers and researchers.</p>",
